        }
      }
    },
    "* 右上角功能菜单，使用示例，分组\n* 单击图片/双击消息全屏查看\n* 全屏查看，翻译，总结，朗读\n* 左滑删除，右滑复制和智能解答。" : {
      "localizations" : {
        "en" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "* Top-right function menu, usage examples, grouping\n* Single-click image/double-click message for full-screen view\n* Full-screen view, translation, summary, reading aloud\n* Swipe left to delete, swipe right to copy and intelligent answer."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "* 右上角功能菜单，使用示例，分组\n* 单击图片/双击消息全屏查看\n* 全屏查看，翻译，总结，朗读\n* 左滑删除，右滑复制和智能解答。"
          }
        }
      }
