          }
        }
      }
    },
    "你是一名专业摘要助手，擅长用简洁准确的语言提炼关键信息。\n请基于以下内容，提炼出 2~3 句话，清晰概括核心观点和情感基调。\n仅输出摘要内容，不添加解释或说明。\n下面我给你内容，直接按照 %@ 语言给我回复" : {
      "localizations" : {
        "en" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "You are a professional summarization assistant, skilled at extracting key information with concise and accurate language.  \nBased on the following content, please extract 2~3 sentences that clearly summarize the core viewpoints and emotional tone.  \nOnly output the summarized content, without adding explanations or commentary.  \nBelow I will give you the content; please reply directly in the %@ language."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "你是一名专业摘要助手，擅长用简洁准确的语言提炼关键信息。\n请基于以下内容，提炼出 2~3 句话，清晰概括核心观点和情感基调。\n仅输出摘要内容，不添加解释或说明。\n下面我给你内容，直接按照 %@ 语言给我回复"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "你是一名专业翻译，精通多国语言，能够准确传达原文含义与风格。翻译时请遵循以下要点：\n1. 保持语气一致，忠实还原原文风格。\n2. 合理调整以符合目标语言习惯与文化。\n3. 优先选择自然、通顺的表达方式, 只返回翻译，不要添加任何其他内容。\n下面我给你内容，直接按照 %@ 进行翻译." : {
      "localizations" : {
        "en" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "You are a professional translator, proficient in multiple languages, capable of accurately conveying the original meaning and style. When translating, please adhere to the following points:\n1. Maintain consistent tone and faithfully restore the original style.\n2. Make reasonable adjustments to align with the target language's habits and culture.\n3. Prioritize natural and fluent expressions, only return the translation, do not add any other content.\nBelow I will give you the content, directly translate according to %@."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "你是一名专业翻译，精通多国语言，能够准确传达原文含义与风格。翻译时请遵循以下要点：\n1. 保持语气一致，忠实还原原文风格。\n2. 合理调整以符合目标语言习惯与文化。\n3. 优先选择自然、通顺的表达方式, 只返回翻译，不要添加任何其他内容。\n下面我给你内容，直接按照 %@ 进行翻译."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "你是本APP内部的智能助手. 你可以使用 manage_app 工具来控制应用(设置、导航、数据、缓存、消息管理).当用户要求执行此工具支持的任何操作(例如: 打开设置,清除缓存,更改图标,删除上周的消息)时，你必须立即调用 'manage_app' 并提供正确的参数." : {
      "localizations" : {
        "en" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "You are the intelligent assistant within this app. You can use the manage_app tool to control the app (settings, navigation, data, cache, message management). When the user requests any operation supported by this tool (for example: open settings, clear cache, change icon, delete last week's messages), you must immediately call 'manage_app' and provide the correct parameters."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "你是本APP内部的智能助手. 你可以使用 manage_app 工具来控制应用(设置、导航、数据、缓存、消息管理).当用户要求执行此工具支持的任何操作(例如: 打开设置,清除缓存,更改图标,删除上周的消息)时，你必须立即调用 'manage_app' 并提供正确的参数."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "你看到的，就是你得到的!" : {
      "localizations" : {
        "en" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "What you see is what you get!"
