        }
      }
    },
    "可选参数值:\n- passive：仅添加到列表，不会亮屏提醒\n- active： 默认值，系统会立即亮屏显示通知。\n- timeSensitive:  时效性通知,专注模式下可显示通知。\n- critical: ‼️重要提醒，静音或专注模式可正常提醒\n* 参数可使用 0-10代替，具体查看文档" : {
      "localizations" : {
        "en" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Optional parameter values:\n- passive: Only added to the list, will not trigger a screen alert.\n- active: Default value, the system will immediately display a notification on screen.\n- timeSensitive: Time-sensitive notification, can display the notification in focus mode.\n- critical: ⚠️ Important alert, can trigger normally in silent or focus mode.\n* Parameters can be replaced with 0-10, refer to the documentation for details."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "可选参数值:\n- passive：仅添加到列表，不会亮屏提醒\n- active： 默认值，系统会立即亮屏显示通知。\n- timeSensitive:  时效性通知,专注模式下可显示通知。\n- critical: ‼️重要提醒，静音或专注模式可正常提醒\n* 参数可使用 0-10代替，具体查看文档"
          }
        }
      }
    },
