    "网络权限是应用正常运行的基础，用于接收推送通知、同步数据和获取最新信息。没有网络权限，应用的核心功能将无法正常工作。" : {
      "localizations" : {
        "en" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Network permissions are essential for the normal operation of the application, used to receive push notifications, synchronize data, and obtain the latest information. Without network permissions, the core functions of the application will be unable to work properly."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
